Tsunami da girgizar ƙasa sun halaka tsibiri a ƙasar Indonesia, kuma sun kashe mutane da yawa
Bayan girgizar ƙasar Lombok, an gaya wa ƙungiyoyin ba da agaji na ƙasashen waje cewa ba a bukatar taimakon su.
Ko da yake an raba fiye da kashi 10 cikin 100 na mutanen tsibirin Lombok, ba a ayyana bala'in a matsayin bala'i na kasa ba, wanda ya zama dole don samun taimakon duniya.
Abin takaici, a lokuta da dama, sun bayyana karara cewa ba sa neman taimakon kasa da kasa, don haka lamarin ya yi wuya sosai, in ji Sumbung.
Ko da yake kungiyar Save the Children na kokarin kafa tawagar da za ta tafi Palu, ba a san ko an ba wa ma'aikatan kasashen waje damar shiga wurin ba.
Sutopo, kakakin hukumar kula da bala'i ta kasa, ya ce hukumomin Indonesia na nazarin halin da ake ciki a Palu don ganin ko hukumomin kasa da kasa za su iya taimakawa wajen kokarin.
Ganin yadda Indonesia ke fama da girgizar kasa a kai a kai, ba za a iya gaskata cewa kasar ba ta shirya don fushin yanayi ba.
Ko da yake an gina wuraren kariya daga tsunami a Aceh, ba a yawan samun su a wasu yankunan bakin teku.
Ya bayyana cewa rashin siginar gargadi na tsunami a Palu, duk da cewa an bayar da gargadi, na iya taimakawa ga asarar rayuka.
Ko da a cikin yanayi mafi kyau, tafiya tsakanin tsibiran Indonesia yana da ƙalubale.
Bala'i yana sa yanayin ya yi wuya.
Wani jirgin asibiti da ya sauka a Lombok don kula da wadanda girgizar kasa ta shafa yana kan hanyarsa ta zuwa Palu, amma zai dauki akalla kwanaki uku kafin ya isa wurin da sabon bala'in ya auku.
Shugaban kasar Joko Widodo ya sanya inganta ingantattun kayayyakin more rayuwa a Indonesia a matsayin babban abin da ya fi mayar da hankali a yakin neman zabensa kuma ya ba da kuɗi da yawa don hanyoyi da layin dogo.
Amma rashin kudade ya shafi gwamnatin Joko, wanda zai shiga wani sabon yakin neman zabe a shekara mai zuwa.
Haka kuma Joko na fuskantar matsin lamba daga bangarorin addinai a Indonesia saboda mambobin musulmi da yawa sun karɓi wani addini mai ra'ayin mazan jiya.
An kashe mutane sama da 1,000 kuma dubun dubatar sun rasa gidajensu yayin da kungiyoyin Krista da Musulmai suka yi fada a tituna, ta amfani da makamai, baka da kibiyoyi, da sauran makamai masu linzami.
Bidiyo: Daniel Sturridge na Liverpool ya zira kwallo ta tsallake raga a wasan da Chelsea
Daniel Sturridge ya ceci Liverpool daga shan kaye a gasar Premier da Chelsea ta hanyar zura kwallo a minti na 89 a filin wasan Stamford Bridge a London a ranar Asabar.
Sturridge ya samu wata wucewa daga Xherdan Shaqiri, yayin da yake kusan mita 30 daga hanyar abokan hamayyarsa, kuma tawagarsa ta jagoranci Chelsea 1-0.
Ya buga kwallon ya tura ta hagu kafin ya buga ta a kan ƙofar.
Kwallon ya isa saman ƙwallon ƙafa, yana zuwa kusurwar dama ta ƙofar.
A ƙarshe, kwallon ta wuce Kepa Arrizabalaga wanda ya yi tsalle zuwa gare ta kuma ya faɗi a ƙofar.
"Ina bukatar in yi kokarin samun matsayi mai kyau, in samu kwallon, kuma 'yan wasa kamar Shaq suna kokarin ci gaba da ci gaba da ci gaba, don haka na yi kokarin samun karin lokaci", in ji Sturridge ga LiverpoolFC.com.
Na ga Kante yana zuwa kuma ya isa, ban yi tunani sosai game da shi ba, kawai na ɗauki kwallon na ci gaba.
Chelsea ta yi gaba da ci 1-0 a lokacin hutu bayan da dan wasan Belgium Eden Hazard ya ci kwallo a minti na 25.
Dan wasan gaba na kungiyar blue ya tura kwallon zuwa Mateo Kovacic, sannan ya koma tsakiyar filin kuma ya tsere zuwa filin Liverpool.
Kovacic ya yi saurin motsawa daya-biyu a tsakiyar filin wasa.
Sai ya tura Hazard kwallon, ta shiga cikin kwando.
Hazard ya wuce tsaron kuma ya tura kwallon cikin raga, yana iya buga ta da kafarsa ta hagu kuma ya wuce dan wasan Liverpool Alisson Becker.
Liverpool za ta kara da Napoli a wasan rukuni na gasar zakarun Turai ranar Laraba da karfe 3 na yamma a filin wasa na Sao Paolo da ke Naples, Italiya.
Chelsea za ta kara da Videoton a gasar cin kofin Europa a ranar Alhamis, da karfe 3:00 na yamma, a birnin London.
Yawan mutanen da tsunami ya kashe a Indonesia ya kai 832
Adadin mutanen da girgizar kasa da tsunami ta kashe a Indonesia ya kai 832, a cewar hukumar bala'i ta kasa da safiyar Lahadi.
Mutane da dama sun makale a karkashin gine-ginen da suka rushe sakamakon girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.5 da ta afku a ranar Juma'a, wanda ya haifar da raƙuman ruwa masu tsawon mita shida, in ji mai magana da yawun hukumar, Sutopo Purwo Nugroho, a wani taron manema labarai.
Birnin Palu, wanda ke da mutane fiye da 380,000, ya cika da tarkace saboda rushewar gine-ginen.
'Yan sanda sun kama wani mutum mai shekaru 32 da haihuwa, wanda ake zargi da kashe wata mata ta hanyar dabara.
An fara bincike kan kisan gillar bayan da aka gano gawar wata mata a Birkenhead, Merseyside a safiyar yau.
