Hoton Cromwell a majalisar ya zama sabon abin tunawa da aka lalata a cikin rikice-rikice game da "rubuce-rikicen tarihi"
Cire shi zai zama adalci mai kyau ga halakar Taliban na al'adun gargajiya da na addini da yawa na Ingila, wanda mabiyanta masu tsattsauran ra'ayi suka yi.
Amma al'ummar Cromwell sun bayyana shawarar Jeremy Crick a matsayin "wauta" da kuma "ƙoƙarin sake rubuta tarihi".
John Goldsmith, shugaban kungiyar Cromwell, ya ce: "Ba makawa a cikin muhawara ta yanzu game da cire mutummutumai cewa siffar Oliver Cromwell daga fadar Westminster ta zama manufa.
Cromwell bai umurci ko kuma ya zartar da ikon da aka yi a yakin basasa na Ingila ba.
Wataƙila zai yi hadaya da Cromwell da ba daidai ba saboda ayyukan kakansa Thomas na ƙarni na baya.
Babban wakilcin Cromwell, wanda Sir William Hamo Thorneycroft ya yi, hujja ce ta ra'ayi na karni na 19 da kuma wani ɓangare na tarihin wani adadi wanda mutane da yawa suka yi imanin ya cancanci bikin.
Goldsmith ya shaida wa jaridar The Sunday Telegraph cewa: Cromwell yana da yawa, watakila a ƙarshen karni na 19 fiye da yadda yake a yau, a matsayin mai kare majalisa daga matsa lamba daga waje, a cikin yanayin, ba shakka, mulkin mallaka.
