Sama da mutane miliyan 20 ne suka kalli sauraron karar Brett Kavanaugh
Sama da mutane miliyan 20 ne suka kalli sanarwar da aka bayar ta hannun wanda zai zama babban alkalin kotun kasar, Brett Kavanaugh, da kuma matar da ta zarge shi da laifin fyade da aka yi a shekarun 1980s, Christine Blasey Ford, a gidajen talabijin shida.
A daidai wannan lokaci, rikicin siyasa ya ci gaba, tare da tashoshin talabijin da ke katse jadawalin yau da Juma'a don wani labari na ƙarshe: yarjejeniyar da Sanata Jeff Flake na Arizona ya yi don FBI ta gudanar da bincike kan zargin, na mako guda.
Ford ta shaida wa kwamitin shari'a cewa ta tabbata 100% cewa Kavanaugh ya zalunce ta yayin da yake cikin maye kuma ya yi ƙoƙarin yin lalata da ita a wani biki na makarantar sakandare.
Kavanaugh, a cikin wata shaida mai zurfi, ya ce ya tabbata 100% cewa wannan bai faru ba.
A cewar Nielsen, mutane sama da miliyan 20.4 ne suka kalli sauraron shari'ar ranar Juma'a.
Kamfanin ya ƙidaya matsakaicin kallo akan CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Ba a samu lambobin nan da nan ga sauran cibiyoyin sadarwa da suka watsa shi ba, ciki har da PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network.
Kuma Nielsen yawanci tana da matsala wajen tantance mutanen da ke kallon ta daga ofishinta.
Don sanya wannan a cikin hangen nesa, wannan masu sauraro ne kamar na wasan kwallon kafa na wasan kwaikwayo ko kuma na Academy Awards.
A cewar Nielsen, Fox News Channel, wanda masu gabatar da jawabai suka goyi bayan nadin Kavanaugh, ya kasance a gaban dukkan tashoshin, tare da matsakaicin masu kallo miliyan 5.69 a lokacin sauraron yau da kullum.
ABC ne na biyu, tare da masu kallo miliyan 3.26.
A cewar Nielsen, mutane miliyan 3.1 ne suka kalli CBS, NBC miliyan 2.94, MSNBC miliyan 2.89 da CNN miliyan 2.52.
Ba a sami ci gaba ba bayan an yi wannan sauraron.
