Bayan ofishin Jamhuriyar Republican ya ba da sanarwar cewa zai kada kuri'ar Kavanaugh, an kama shi a kyamarorin CNN da CBS a safiyar ranar Juma'a yayin da masu zanga-zangar ke ihu da shi kuma yana ƙoƙarin hawa lif zuwa taron Kwamitin Shari'a.
