Halin wasansu da kuma tawagar ba su canza ba tun lokacin da suka dawo saman, amma dole ne a ba Holt yabo ga yadda ya horar da tawagar tun lokacin da ya karbe ta.
Yana da mutane da yawa da ya kamata ya bi misalinsa.
Kyaftin Halkett ya yi kyau, tare da kyakkyawan tsari na tsaro, yayin da Menga ya sa Connor Goldson da Joe Worrall cikin matsala a cikin wasan.
Amma 'yan wasan Rangers ba su da wahayi sosai.
Duk da cewa sun yi aiki mai kyau a lokacin da Gerrard ke jagorantar su, amma ba su kai matsayin da suka yi ba.
An kasa cin kwallo, sun samu nasarar kama ƙofar abokan hamayyarsu sau ɗaya, kuma wannan ya zama alamar faɗakarwa ga Rangers, waɗanda ke tsakiyar jerin.
Sakamakon binciken da aka yi a Köln ya nuna cewa, akwai wasu abubuwa da suka faru a lokacin da aka kai ziyarar.
Duk abin da ya kasance mai kyau a ranar Asabar (29 ga Satumba) lokacin da shugabannin Turkiyya da Jamus suka hadu a Berlin don karin kumallo.
Yau ce rana ta karshe da shugaba Erdogan ya kai ziyara Jamus domin daidaita dangantaka tsakanin kasashen da ke da kawancen NATO.
Sun nuna rashin jin daɗi game da batutuwan da suka shafi 'yancin bil adama, 'yancin' yan jarida da kuma kasancewa cikin Tarayyar Turai.
A wannan yanayin, Erdogan ya tafi Cologne don buɗe sabon babban masallaci.
Birnin yana da mafi yawan 'yan Turkiyya a duniya, a waje da Turkiyya.
'Yan sanda sun yi amfani da dalilai na tsaro don hana taron mutane 25,000 daga taruwa a gaban masallacin, amma masu goyon baya da yawa sun taru a kusa da su don ganin shugaban.
Daruruwan masu zanga-zangar adawa da Erdogan, mafi yawansu Kurdawa, sun yi magana, suna la'antar manufofin Erdogan da kuma shawarar da gwamnatin Jamus ta yanke na maraba da shi da hannu biyu a kasar.
Wannan zanga-zangar ta nuna bambancin da ke tsakanin wani baƙo da wasu Turkawa a Jamus ke ganin gwarzo ne da kuma wani mai mulkin mallaka.
Hadarin mota a Deptford: wani mai hawan keke ya mutu bayan ya yi karo da wata mota
Wani mai hawan keke ya mutu bayan ya yi karo da wata mota a London.
Hadarin ya faru ne a mahadar titin Bestwood da Evelyn Street, wata babbar titi a Deptford, a kudu maso gabashin garin, da misalin karfe 10:15 na dare.
Direban motar ya tsaya, kuma jami'an jinya sun kai ga wurin hatsarin, amma mutumin ya mutu a wurin.
Hadarin ya zo ne watanni kadan bayan da wani mai hawan keke ya mutu a wani hatsari da ya faru a kan titin Childers Street, inda direban ya gudu daga wurin, wanda ke da nisan mil daya daga inda hatsarin ya faru a ranar Asabar.
'Yan sanda sun ce jami'an na kokarin gano mutumin da kuma sanar da danginsa.
An hana zirga-zirgar ababen hawa zuwa yankin, an kuma sauya hanyar zirga-zirgar motoci, kuma an shawarci masu babura da su guji yankin.
Gidan yarin Long Lartin: jami'an tsaro shida sun ji rauni a wani rikici
Jami'an gidan yarin guda shida sun ji rauni a wani rikici a wata kurkuku mai tsaron maza, in ji wani jami'in gidan yarin.
A ranar Lahadi, an samu wani rikici a HMP Long Martin da ke Worcestershire da misalin karfe 9:30.
An kawo jami'an tsaro don magance rikicin da ya shafi fursunoni takwas, wadanda aka ware a wani reshe.
Jami'an sun samu magani a wurin saboda raunuka a fuskokinsu.
Wani kakakin gidan yarin ya ce: An nemi taimakon kwararrun ma'aikatan gidan yarin don magance wani lamari da ke gudana a HMP Long Lartin.
Ma'aikatan jirgin sun samu sauki bayan sun ji rauni.
Ba mu yarda da tashin hankali a gidajen yarinmu ba kuma muna da dokoki masu kyau game da waɗanda ke da alhakin, waɗanda za a tura su ga 'yan sanda kuma za su iya yin tsawon lokaci a kurkuku.
HMP Long Lartin tana da fursunoni sama da 500, ciki har da wasu daga cikin masu laifi mafiya hatsari a kasar.
A watan Yuni, an bayar da rahoton cewa gwamnan gidan yarin ya bukaci asibiti bayan wani fursuna ya kai masa hari.
A watan Oktoba na bara, an kira jami'an tsaro da ke kula da rikici zuwa kurkuku don magance wani yanayi mai tsanani, inda aka kai wa ma'aikatan hari da ƙwallon pool.
Phoenix, Las Vegas, Salt Lake City suna cikin hatsarin ambaliyar ruwa saboda guguwar Rosa (yankuna masu bushewa na iya jin daɗin fa'idodi saboda wannan)
Ba kasafai ake samun wani yanayi mai zafi a Arizona ba, amma wannan yana iya faruwa a farkon mako mai zuwa, saboda sauran albarkatun makamashi na Hurricane Rosa za a yi amfani da su a cikin hamadar kudu maso yamma, yana haifar da haɗarin ambaliyar ruwa da sauri.
Hukumar Kula da Yanayi ta Kasa ta riga ta ba da gargadin ambaliyar ruwa mai saurin zuwa Litinin da Talata a yammacin Arizona, kudu da gabashin Nevada, kudu maso gabashin California da Utah, gami da Phoenix, Flagstaff, Las Vegas da Salt Lake City.
Ana sa ran Rosa za ta kai Phoenix a ranar Talata, kuma za ta yi ruwan sama a ranar Litinin.
Hukumar Kula da Yanayi ta Phoenix ta sanar a shafinta na Twitter cewa, 'yan guguwa 10 ne kawai suka yi hadari ko kuma sanyin yanayi a cikin nisan mil 200 daga Phoenix tun daga shekarar 1950!
Katrina (1967) wani guguwa ne da ke aiki a cikin nisan kilomita 60 daga iyakar Arizona.
Sabbin tsarin da Cibiyar Guguwa ta Kasa ta samar na hasashen ruwan sama mai tsawon inci 5 zuwa 10, tare da wasu adadi na inci 15 a Mogollon Rim na Arizona.
A wasu yankunan kudu maso yammacin hamada, ciki har da tsakiyar Rocky Mountains da Great Basin, za a yi rikodin tsakanin 3 zuwa 5 cm, tare da yiwuwar jimlar har zuwa 10 cm a yankunan da ke kewaye.
Ga yankunan da ba su da haɗarin ambaliyar ruwa, ruwan sama da Rosa zai iya zama albarka, tun da yake yankin yana fama da fari.
Ko da yake ambaliyar ruwa tana da tsanani sosai, a wasu wurare, ruwan sama mai yawa zai taimaka, domin kudu maso yammacin ƙasar na fama da fari.
A cewar Hukumar Kula da Fari ta Amurka, sama da kashi 40 cikin dari na Arizona suna fuskantar fari mafi muni, wato kashi na biyu mafi girma, kamar yadda weather.com ta bayyana.
Da farko, guguwar Rosa za ta haifar da ambaliyar ƙasa a yankin Baja California da ke ƙasar Mexico.
Rosa, wanda har yanzu yana da ƙarfin guguwa a safiyar Lahadi, tare da iskar da ta kai kilomita 136 a kowace awa, yana da nisan mil 620 a kudancin Punta Eugenia, Mexico, kuma yana tafiya arewacin kilomita 19 a kowace awa.
Guguwar za ta haɗu da ruwan sanyi a cikin Pacific kuma saboda haka zai ragu.
An yi hasashen cewa za a yi ambaliyar ƙasa a ƙasar Mexico kuma za ta zama guguwa mai ƙarfi a ranar Litinin da yamma.
Ruwan sama mai yawa a Mexico na iya zama mai mahimmanci, yana haifar da haɗarin ambaliyar ruwa.
Ana sa ran ruwan sama mai yawan inci 8 zuwa 10 daga Baja California zuwa arewa maso yammacin Sonora, kuma zai iya kaiwa inci 25, a cewar weather.com.
Bayan haka, Rosa za ta koma arewa zuwa Mexico a matsayin guguwar da ta kai iyakar Arizona a safiyar Talata a matsayin guguwar da ta kai Arizona kuma za ta kai kudancin Utah a daren Talata.
"Babban haɗarin da Rosa ko kuma abin da ya rage daga cikinta shi ne ruwan sama mai yawa a Baja California, arewa maso yammacin Sonora da kuma hamadar kudu maso yammacin Amurka", in ji wani jami'in Hukumar Kula da Guguwa ta Amirka.
Ana tsammanin wannan ruwan sama zai haifar da ambaliyar ruwa, wanda zai yi barazanar rayuwar mutane, kuma ya kawo kwararar shara a cikin hamada, da kuma ambaliyar ƙasa a cikin yankunan tsaunuka.
An kama mutane hudu da laifin kisan kai a garin Midsomer Norton
An kama wasu matasa uku da wani mutum mai shekaru 20 a kan zargin yunkurin kisan kai bayan da aka samu wata 'yar shekara 16 da raunukan wuka a Somerset.
An gano matashin da raunuka a yankin Excelsior Terrace da ke Midsomer Norton a misalin karfe 4 na safiyar Asabar.
An kai shi asibiti inda yake cikin koshin lafiya.
An kama wani yaro dan shekara 17, da biyu 'yan shekara 18 da daya dan shekara 20 a yankin Radstock a daren jiya, a cewar 'yan sandan Avon da Somerset.
