Gendon ya bayyana yadda, sa'o'i kadan bayan da aka watsa labarin faduwar otal din Roa Roa a cikin al'ummar masu wasan motsa jiki, ya aika da sakonnin WhatsApp ga masu fafatawa a Palu da ke halartar bikin da aka shirya a bakin rairayin bakin teku.
Amma a gaban saƙonnin da ya aika, babu wasu shuɗi biyu sai ɗaya kawai.
