Wasu 'yan fashi sun sace dala 26,750 yayin da suke cajin kudi a wata ATM a Newport on the Levee
A safiyar ranar Juma'a, 'yan fashi sun sace dala 26,750 daga ma'aikacin kamfanin Brink da ke aiki a wata na'urar ATM a Newport on the Levee, a cewar wata sanarwa da 'yan sanda suka fitar.
Direban motar ya kwashe ATM a wurin shakatawa kuma yana shirin fitar da karin kudi, Dennis McCarthy ya rubuta a cikin sanarwar.
Yayin da yake aiki, wani mutum ya gudu daga bayan ma'aikacin Brink kuma ya sace jakar da ke dauke da kudi da za a kawo.
A cewar sanarwar, shaidu sun lura da wasu mutane da dama da ake zargi da guduwa daga wurin, amma 'yan sanda ba su ambaci yawan mutanen da ke cikin lamarin ba.
