Kit Harington, tauraruwar wasan kwaikwayo na Game of Thrones, ta kai hari ga mutum mai guba
Kit Harington sananne ne saboda rawar Jon Snow a cikin mummunan wasan kwaikwayo na zamani na wasan kwaikwayo na HBO.
Amma ɗan wasan mai shekara 31 ya yi wa jarumin da ke nuna halin nuna bambanci yaƙi, yana cewa nuna irin waɗannan halayen a kan allon yana sa yara maza su yi tunanin cewa dole ne su kasance masu tsauri don a girmama su.
A wata hira da The Sunday Times Culture, Kit ya ce yana jin cewa "wani abu ya faru ba daidai ba" kuma ya yi mamakin yadda za a magance matsalar cutarwa a cikin zamanin #MeToo.
Kit, wanda ya yi aure kwanan nan da Rose Leslie, 'yar wasan kwaikwayo ta Game of Thrones, wadda take shekara 31, ta ce tana "daurewa" ta yi magana game da wannan batun.
