Wata majiya a cikin jagorancin Jam'iyyar Labour ta shaida wa jaridar The Sunday Times cewa: "Ana sa ran sanarwar game da sake duba manufofin kafin karshen shekara.
Ba zai faru ba cikin dare, amma aikin kwana hudu a mako shine kyakkyawan buri a cikin tsarin jam'iyyar na daidaita tattalin arzikin ga ma'aikata, da kuma tsarin jam'iyyar gaba daya game da masana'antu.
Jam'iyyar Labour ba ita ce ta farko da ta goyi bayan wannan ra'ayin ba; mako na kwana hudu na aiki ya kasance daya daga cikin alkawuran Jam'iyyar Green Party a yakin neman zaben shekara ta 2017.
Duk da haka, wannan burin ba shi da goyon baya daga dukan Labour Party.
