Amurka na iya amfani da sojojin ruwa wajen 'kulle' da zai kawo cikas ga kayayyakin da Rasha ke fitarwa na makamashi, in ji sakataren harkokin cikin gida
Washington na iya, idan ya cancanta, amfani da sojojin ruwa don hana makamashin Rasha isa wasu kasuwannin ciki har da Gabas ta Tsakiya, in ji Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida Ryan Zinke, kamar yadda Washington Examiner ta ruwaito.
Zinke ya yi ikirarin cewa, shigar da Rasha cikin Syria, musamman ma inda take aiki a gayyatar da gwamnatin da ta dace, wata hujja ce ta gano sabbin kasuwannin makamashi.
Ina ganin dalilin da yasa nake Gabas ta Tsakiya shine don in shiga tsakani wajen sayar da makamashi, kamar yadda nake yi a Gabashin Turai da kudancin Turai, in ji shi.
Kuma a cewar jami'in, akwai hanyoyi da hanyoyin da za a bi da lamarin.
"Amurka tana da ikon, ta hanyar sojojin ruwanmu, don tabbatar da cewa hanyoyin ruwa suna budewa kuma, idan ya cancanta, don kafa wani shinge, don hana makamashi shiga kasuwa", in ji shi.
Zinke ya yi jawabi ga mahalarta taron da kungiyar Consumer Energy Alliance ta shirya, wata kungiya mai zaman kanta da ke bayyana kanta a matsayin "muryar mai amfani da makamashi" a Amurka.
Ya ci gaba da kwatanta yadda Washington ke hulɗa da Rasha da Iran, yana nuna cewa tsarin yana da kusan iri ɗaya.
"Zaɓin tattalin arziki ga Iran da Rasha shine, fiye da ƙasa, amfani da maye gurbin man fetur", in ji shi, yana cewa Rasha ta san dabara guda ɗaya saboda tattalin arzikinta na tushen burbushin halittu.
