A wannan bangaren, wakilan gwamnatin Trump, ciki har da Shugaba Donald Trump, suna kokarin shawo kan Jamus ta janye daga aikin "da bai dace ba" na bututun gas na Nord Stream 2, wanda a cewar Trump zai mayar da Berlin "kurkuku" ga Moscow.
Moscow ta sha jaddada cewa aikin dalar Amurka biliyan 11 na bututun Nord Stream 2, wanda zai ninka karfin bututun da ke akwai zuwa mita biliyan 110 na bututun, aikin tattalin arziki ne kawai.
