A lokacin taron da aka yi a birnin Holyoke, Massachusetts, Warren ya tabbatar da cewa yana tunanin neman takara.
"Lokaci ya yi da mace za ta je Washington ta gyara gwamnatinmu da ta lalace, kuma hakan na bukatar mace mai karfi", in ji ta, a cewar The Hill.
Bayan 6 ga watan Nuwamba, zan yi tunani sosai game da ko zan tsaya takarar shugaban kasa.
Warren ya kuma yi magana game da Shugaba Donald Trump a lokacin taron da aka yi a birnin, yana cewa ya "ja ƙasar cikin hanyar da ba daidai ba".
"Ina matukar damuwa da abin da Donald Trump ke yi wa dimokiradiyarmu", in ji ta.
Warren ya kasance mai sukar Trump da Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya zaba don Kotun Koli.
A wani sakon da ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter ranar Juma'a, Warren ya ce "a dabi'ance muna bukatar binciken FBI kafin zabe".
Duk da haka, wani binciken da aka buga a ranar Alhamis ya nuna cewa yawancin masu jefa kuri'ar Warren ba su yi imani ya kamata ya tsaya takara a 2020 ba.
Kashi hamsin da takwas na masu jefa kuri'a a Massachusetts sun ce bai kamata Sanatan ya tsaya takara ba, a cewar wani binciken da Cibiyar Nazarin Siyasa ta Jami'ar Suffolk/Boston Globe ta gudanar.
Kashi talatin da biyu cikin dari na masu amsa sun goyi bayan irin wannan takarar.
Binciken ya nuna ƙarin goyon baya ga takarar tsohon gwamna Deval Patrick: 38% na masu amsa suna goyon bayan yiwuwar takararsa kuma 48% suna adawa.
Sauran sunayen wasu sanannun 'yan Democrat da za su iya tsayawa takara a 2020 sune Mataimakin Shugaban kasa Joe Biden da Bernie Sanders, Sanata daga Vermont.
Biden ya ce zai yanke shawara a hukumance kafin watan Janairu, in ji Associated Press.
Sarah Palin tana magana game da ciwon damuwa na bayan-tashin hankali wanda Track Palin ke fama da shi, a taron Donald Trump
Track Palin, mai shekara 26, ya shafe shekara guda a Iraki bayan ya shiga aikin soja a watan Satumba.
A ranar Litinin da yamma, an kama shi kuma an tuhume shi da aikata wani mummunan aiki a cikin gida.
"Abin da ɗana ya shiga, abin da ya shiga tun lokacin da ya dawo... Zan iya fahimtar wahalar sauran iyalai da ke fama da ciwon tashin hankali da kuma raunukan da sojojinmu ke dawowa da su", in ji ta ga taron jama'a a Tulsa, Oklahoma.
Palin ta kira wannan kama "giwan da ke cikin dakin" kuma ta ce ɗanta da sauran tsoffin sojoji "sun dawo da ɗan bambanci, sun dawo da wuya, suna mamakin ko akwai girmamawa ga abin da su da sojojin su da na jirgin sama, da sauran membobin Sojojin suka yi wa ƙasarsu".
An kama shi a ranar Litinin a Wasilla, Alaska, kuma an tuhume shi da aikata laifin cin zarafin wata mata, hana bayar da rahoton wani mummunan aiki da kuma mallakar bindiga a cikin maye, a cewar Dan Bennett, mai magana da yawun ofishin 'yan sanda na Wasilla.
Jihohi 18 da Gundumar Columbia sun kalubalanci sabuwar manufar neman mafaka
Jihohi 18 da gundumar Columbia sun goyi bayan ƙalubalan doka game da sabuwar manufar Amurka ta hana ba da mafaka ga waɗanda ke ƙoƙarin tserewa daga tashin hankali ko tashin hankali na gida.
Wakilan jihohi 18 da na gundumar sun gabatar da wata takardar neman izinin shiga Amurka a ranar Juma'a a Washington don bayar da goyon baya ga kalubalen da ake yi game da manufofin neman mafaka, in ji NBC News.
Ba a bayyana cikakken sunan mai shigar da kara a shari'ar Grace v. Sessions da kungiyar kare hakkin bil adama ta Amurka ta gabatar a watan Agusta ba.
Ta ce abokin aikinta da 'ya'yansa maza masu nuna tashin hankali, 'yan kungiyar' sun ci zarafinta, amma jami'an Amurka sun ƙi ta neman mafaka a ranar 20 ga Yuli.
An tsare ta a Texas.
Lauyan da gwamnati ta naɗa da ke wakiltar Grace ya kwatanta El Salvador, Honduras da Guatemala, waɗanda suka kawo masu neman mafaka da yawa zuwa Amurka, a matsayin ƙasashe da ke fama da matsalar gangs da kuma tashin hankali a cikin gida.
Sabuwar manufar Amurka ta neman mafaka ta soke hukuncin da Hukumar Kula da Shige da Fice ta yanke a shekarar 2014 wanda ya baiwa 'yan ci-rani da ba su da takardun da ke neman mafaka daga tashin hankali a gida damar neman mafaka.
Babban lauyan yankin Columbia, Karl Racine, ya bayyana a ranar Juma'a cewa sabuwar manufar ta "yi watsi da shekarun da suka gabata na dokokin jihohi, tarayya da na duniya".
"Dokar tarayya ta ce duk bukatar neman mafaka dole ne a yanke ta bisa ga takamaiman gaskiya da yanayin da ake nema, kuma irin wannan iyakancewa ya sabawa wannan ƙa'idar", in ji takardar neman mafaka.
Bugu da ƙari, lauyoyi a cikin takardar sun yi jayayya cewa manufar hana baƙi shiga ta shafi tattalin arzikin Amurka, suna cewa sun fi dacewa su zama 'yan kasuwa kuma su samar da ma'aikata masu dacewa.
Jeff Sessions, babban lauyan Amurka, ya umarci alƙalan shige da fice a watan Yuni da su daina ba da mafaka ga waɗanda ke ƙoƙarin tserewa daga cin zarafin ƙungiyoyi da tashin hankali.
"Ana ba da mafaka ga waɗanda suka bar ƙasarsu saboda tsanantawa ko tsoron nuna bambanci saboda launin fata, addini, ƙasa ko ƙungiyar zamantakewa ko ra'ayi na siyasa", in ji Sessions a ranar 11 ga Yuni, lokacin da ya sanar da manufar.
Matsayin mafaka ba shine magance dukkan matsalolin da mutane ke fuskanta a kowace rana ba, ba ma duk manyan matsalolin ba.
An yi gaggawar ceto a Palu inda mutuwar mutane ta ninka, a cikin tseren lokaci don neman waɗanda suka tsira
Amma ga waɗanda suka tsira, yanayin ya ci gaba da taɓarɓarewa.
"Halin ya yi muni sosai", in ji Risa Kusuma, wata mahaifiya mai shekara 35, da ke kwantar da jaririnta da ke fama da zazzabi a cibiyar kwashe mutane a birnin Palu da ya lalace.
Ambulans suna kawo gawawwaki a kai a kai.
Ruwa mai kyau bai isa ba.
Mazauna sun fara komawa gidajen da aka lalata da kuma shirya kayan da suka ambaliya, suna kokarin ceto duk abin da za a iya ceto.
Daruruwan mutane sun ji rauni, asibitoci da girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.5 ta lalata sun zama marasa amfani.
Wasu daga cikin wadanda suka ji rauni, ciki har da Dwi Haris, wanda ya ji rauni a cikin kashin baya da kuma kafada, suna hutawa a waje da asibitin soja a Palu, inda ake kula da marasa lafiya a waje saboda tsananin tashin hankali.
Ya yi kuka sosai sa'ad da ya tuna yadda girgizar ƙasar ta girgiza ɗakinsa na biyar da matarsa da 'yarsa suke zama.
Ba mu sami lokacin da za mu ceci kanmu ba.
Na kasance a cikin ganuwar bango, ina tsammanin", in ji Harris ga Associated Press, yana mai cewa danginsa suna cikin gari don bikin aure.
Na ji matata ta yi kuka don taimako, sannan kuma kawai shiru.
Ban san abin da ya faru da ita da kuma ɗana ba.
Ina fatan suna lafiya.
Jakadan Amurka ya zargi China da amfani da tallace-tallace na farfaganda
Mako guda bayan da wata jaridar kasar Sin ta wallafa wani shafi hudu a wata jaridar Amurka da ke yabon amfanin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China, jakadan Amurka a China ya zargi Beijing da amfani da kafofin yada labaran Amurka wajen yada farfaganda.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi magana a ranar Laraba game da karin kudin da kasar Sin ta biya jaridar Des Moines Register, jaridar da ta fi sayarwa a Iowa, bayan da ya zargi kasar Sin da tsoma baki a zaben majalisar dattijai na ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba, zargin da kasar Sin ta musanta.
Zargin da ake yi wa Beijing na kokarin tsoma baki a zaben Amurka ya nuna abin da jami'an Amurka suka fadawa Reuters cewa sabon mataki ne a wani yunkuri da Washington ke yi na matsa lamba kan kasar Sin.
Ko da yake al'ada ce ga gwamnatocin kasashen waje su rika tallata tallace-tallace na kasuwanci, Beijing da Washington a yanzu haka suna cikin yakin cinikayya da ke kara tsanantawa, wanda ya kunshi hauhawar harajin shigo da kayayyaki.
Kudaden harajin da China ta kakaba a farkon yakin cinikayya an tsara su ne domin cutar da masu fitar da kayayyaki daga jihohi kamar Iowa, wadanda suka goyi bayan jam'iyyar Trump ta Republican, in ji masana a kasar Sin da Amurka.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a China kuma tsohon gwamnan Iowa, babban mai fitar da kayayyakin gona zuwa China, ya ce Beijing ta cutar da ma'aikata, manoma da 'yan kasuwa na Amurka.
A wata mujallar jaridar Des Moines Register a ranar Lahadi, Branstad ya rubuta cewa China "tana ci gaba da wannan cin zarafin ta hanyar buga tallace-tallace na farfaganda a cikin 'yan jaridunmu".
Da yake yada farfaganda ta hanyar buga wani talla a jaridar Des Moines Register, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta saba wa al'adun Amurka na 'yancin fadin albarkacin baki da kuma 'yancin manema labarai, in ji Branstad.
"A akasin haka, a kan gidan jarida a kan titin nan na Beijing za ku ga muryoyin 'yan adawa kaɗan kuma ba za ku ga ainihin ra'ayoyin da 'yan kasar Sin ke da shi game da mummunan yanayin tattalin arzikin kasar Sin ba, saboda kafofin watsa labarai suna karkashin ikon jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin", in ji shi.
Ya kara da cewa, wata babbar jarida a kasar Sin ta ki buga labarinta, duk da cewa bai bayyana jaridar da ya rubuta ba.
'Yan Republican sun yi watsi da mata kafin zaben tsakiyar shekara saboda badakalar Kavanaugh, manazarta sun yi gargadin
Saboda yawancin manyan 'yan Republican suna goyon baya da kuma kare Brett Kavanaugh, wanda aka zaba a Kotun Koli, daga zargin cin zarafin jima'i, masu sharhi sun yi gargadin cewa za a sami matsala, musamman daga mata, a lokacin zaben tsakiyar shekara mai zuwa.
Motsin zuciyar da wannan abin kunya ya haifar ya kasance mai ƙarfi sosai, kuma yawancin 'yan Republican da suka tattauna shi a fili suna shirin ci gaba da jefa kuri'a.
"Ba za a manta da irin wannan martani ba", in ji Grant Reeher, farfesa a fannin siyasa a Makarantar Maxwell ta Jami'ar Syracuse, ga The Hill a wata kasida da aka buga a ranar Asabar.
Reeher ya ce yana da shakku cewa matakin karshe na Sanata Jeff Flake (Shugaban Arizona) game da binciken FBI zai kwantar da hankalin masu jefa kuri'a masu fushi.
"Mata ba za su manta da abin da ya faru jiya ba, ba za su manta da gobe ba kuma ba za su manta da Nuwamba ba", in ji Karine Jean-Pierre, babban mai ba da shawara da kuma mai magana da yawun kungiyar a ranar Juma'a, a cewar jaridar Washington, D.C.
A safiyar ranar Juma'a, masu zanga-zangar sun yi ihu "Nuwamba ta zo!" yayin da suke zanga-zanga a zauren majalisar dattijai lokacin da 'yan Republican da ke kula da kwamitin shari'a suka zabi ci gaba da zaben Kavanaugh duk da shaidar Dr. Christine Blasey Ford, Mic ta ruwaito.
"Democrats za su kasance masu himma da himma", in ji Stu Rothenberg, wani mai nazarin siyasa na shafin yanar gizon.
Mutane sun ce sun riga sun girma sosai kuma gaskiya ne.
Amma zai iya zama mafi girma, musamman tsakanin mata masu jefa kuri'a a cikin unguwannin da ke kewaye da su da kuma matasa masu shekaru 18 zuwa 29 waɗanda, duk da cewa ba sa son shugaban kasa, ba sa yawan jefa kuri'a.
Tun kafin shaidar Ford ta bayyana zargin cin zarafin da aka yi wa wanda ya nemi gurbin a kotun koli, manazarta sun nuna cewa za a iya fuskantar kalubale idan 'yan Republican suka ci gaba da tabbatar da shi.
"Wannan ya zama abin damuwa ga 'yan Republican", in ji Michael Steele, tsohon shugaban kwamitin Republican National Committee, a farkon makon da ya gabata, a cewar NBC News.
"Ba wai kawai batun zaben kwamitin ba ne ko kuma na karshe ko kuma yiwuwar tabbatar da Kavanaugh, amma yadda 'yan Republican suka bi da wannan lamarin da kuma yadda suka bi da ita", in ji Guy Cecil, darektan Priorities USA, wata kungiyar tallafawa zaben 'yan Democrat, ga tashar labarai.
Duk da haka, jama'ar Amirka sun rarrabu sosai game da abin da za su gaskata daga shaidar Ford da Kavanaugh: mutane da yawa sun gaskata da na biyun.
Wani sabon bincike da YouGov ya yi ya nuna cewa kashi 41 cikin dari na masu amsa sun yi imani da gaske ko kuma sun yi imani da cewa shaidar Ford ta kasance gaskiya, yayin da kashi 35 cikin dari suka ce sun yi imani da gaske ko kuma cewa shaidar Kavanaugh na iya zama gaskiya.
Bugu da ƙari, kashi 38 cikin ɗari sun ce Kavanaugh ya yi ƙarya, wataƙila ko tabbas, yayin da kashi 30 cikin ɗari kawai suka faɗi haka game da Ford.
Bayan Flake, FBI na binciken zargin da Ford ya yi, da kuma aƙalla wani mutum, Deborah Ramirez, The Guardian ta ruwaito.
A makon da ya gabata, Ford ta shaida a gaban kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattijai cewa Kavanaugh ya yi mata fyade lokacin da take da shekaru 17.
Ramirez ta yi zargin cewa wanda aka zaba a Kotun Koli ya nuna al'aurarsa a gabanta lokacin da suke halartar wani biki a lokacin da suke dalibai a Yale a shekarun 1980.
Wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo mai fadi ya shirya kafa sabuwar yanar gizo domin karawa Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo, ya kaddamar da wani kamfani da zai gasa da Facebook da Amazon da Google.
Sabon aikin almara na fasaha, Inrupt, kamfani ne wanda ya dogara da Solid, dandamali na buɗe tushen Berners-Lee.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda aka adana bayanan su da kuma wanda ke da damar samun damar bayanin.
A wata hira ta musamman da Fast Company, Berners-Lee yayi dariya cewa manufar da ke bayan Inrupt shine "mulkin duniya".
"Yanzu dole ne mu yi hakan", ya yi magana game da farawa.
Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi.
Aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasahar Solid don bawa mutane damar ƙirƙirar nasu Kundin Bayanai na Kan layi ko PODs.
Yana iya ƙunsar jerin sunayen lambobin sadarwa, shirye-shirye, kalandarku, ɗakunan karatu na kiɗa ko wasu kayan aiki na sirri da na sana'a.
Kamar dai Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify duk suna cikin burauzar guda, duk a lokaci daya.
Abin da ke da ban mamaki game da wannan bayanan sirri na kan layi shine mai amfani yana da cikakken iko akan wanda zai iya samun damar irin wannan bayanin.
Kamfanin ya kira wannan "haɓakawar mutum ta hanyar bayanai".
A cewar shugaban kamfanin, John Bruce, manufar ita ce Inrupt ya ba da albarkatu, matakai da ƙwarewa masu dacewa, don haka ya sa kowa ya sami damar amfani da Solid.
A halin yanzu, kamfanin ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani dandamali na tsaro da IBM ta saya, ƙungiyar masu haɓaka da ke aiki a kan aikin, da kuma ƙungiyar masu shirye-shiryen sa kai.
Tun daga wannan makon, masu haɓaka fasaha a duk faɗin duniya za su iya ƙirƙirar aikace-aikacen da aka rarraba ta amfani da kayan aikin da ke kan gidan yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba sa magana da Facebook da Google kan ko su kawo sauyi gaba daya idan tsarin kasuwancin su ya rikita batun.
Ba ma neman izinin su.
A wani rubutu da aka buga a ranar Asabar a shafin Medium, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa Mashin Inrupt shine samar da wutar lantarki ta kasuwanci da kuma tsarin halittu wanda zai taimaka wajen kare mutuncin da ingancin sabuwar Intanet a Solid.
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya kawo sauyi a yanar gizo lokacin da ya kirkiro kungiyar World Wide Web Consortium a MIT.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya kasance mai tasiri a cikin muhawara game da tsaka tsaki na Intanet.
Ko da bayan ya kaddamar da Inrupt, Berners-Lee zai kasance mai kafa da kuma darektan Cibiyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya, Cibiyar Yanar Gizo da Cibiyar Bayanai ta Buɗe.
"Ina da kwarin gwiwa game da wannan zamani na gaba na Intanet", in ji Berners-Lee.
Bernard Vann: limamin da ya lashe Gicciye na Nasara a yakin duniya na farko an yi bikin
Limamin cocin Anglican daya tilo da ya lashe lambar yabo ta Victoria Cross a yakin duniya na farko an yi bikin ne a garinsa bayan shekaru 100.
Laftanar da Colonel Reverend Bernard Vann ya lashe lambar yabo a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918 a lokacin da aka kai hari a Bellenglise da Lehaucourt.
Ya mutu ne bayan kwana hudu, kuma bai san cewa an ba shi lambar yabo ta soji mafi girma ba.
An bayyana wani dutse na tunawa da shi a ranar Asabar da jikokinsa biyu a lokacin da ake gudanar da fareti a Rushden, Northamptonshire.
Ɗaya daga cikin jikokinsa, Michael Vann, ya ce "abin mamaki ne da alama" cewa za a bayyana dutsen daidai shekaru 100 bayan da kakansa ya lashe lambar yabo.
A cewar London Gazette, a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, Lieutenant Colonel Vann ya jagoranci rundunarsa a kan Canal de Saint-Quentin "a cikin hazo mai yawa da kuma wuta mai tsanani da kuma bindigogi".
Daga baya, ya yi gaggawa zuwa layin gaba kuma, tare da "ƙarfin hali mai ban mamaki", ya buɗe hanyar sojojin, sannan ya kai hari kan wani gidan bindiga shi kaɗai kuma ya sami nasarar kawar da wasu makamai uku na rukunin.
An kashe Lieutenant Colonel Vann da wani dan wasan Jamus a ranar 4 ga Oktoba, 1918, wata daya kafin karshen yakin.
Michael Vann, mai shekara 72, ya ce ayyukan kakansa "abu ne da na san ba zan taɓa iya yin daidai da shi ba, amma hakan ya sa na kasance da tawali'u".
Shi da ɗan'uwansa, Dr. James Vann, sun kuma sanya kambi bayan bikin, wanda Orchestra na Matasa na Brentwood Imperial ya jagoranci.
Michael Vann ya ce "yana jin matukar girmamawa da taka rawa a cikin bikin" kuma ya kara da cewa "darajar jarumi na gaske ana nuna ta ne da goyon bayan da mutane da yawa ke ba shi".
MMA magoya baya sun zauna a farke duk dare don ganin Bellator 206 amma an basu zane mai ban dariya na Peppa Pig a madadin
Ka yi tunanin cewa ka yi barci dukan dare kana kallon Bellator 206, wani abu mai ɗauke da taurari da yawa, amma ba ka iya kallon babban abu ba.
