Da karfe 6 na safe, daidai lokacin da Gegard Mousasi ke shirin fuskantar Rory MacDonald, masu kallo a Burtaniya sun yi mamakin lokacin da aka maye gurbin watsa shirye-shiryen da wani labarin Peppa Pig.
Wasu ba su gamsu ba domin sun yi barci duk dare suna kallon wasan.
Wani mai goyon baya ya bayyana a shafin Twitter cewa sauya zuwa zane-zane na yara "wani irin mummunan wasa ne".
"Dokar gwamnati ta ce wannan abun ba shi da kyau a karfe 6 na safe, don haka dole ne su canza zuwa shirye-shiryen yara", in ji Dave Schwartz, babban mataimakin shugaban Bellator na kasuwanci da sadarwa, lokacin da aka tambaye shi game da watsa shirye-shiryen.
Peppa Piggy, haka ne.
