"Lokacin da na yi tunani game da sakewa, ina tunanin za mu iya warwarewa", in ji Coker.
Amma safiya shida ce a ranar Lahadi a nan kuma ba za mu iya yin hakan ba sai ranar Lahadi, lokacinmu, ko Litinin, lokacin su.
Amma muna aiki a kan hakan.
Ku yi imani da ni, lokacin da aka canza jadawalin, na fara samun saƙonnin rubutu da yawa kuma ba duka ne abokantaka ba.
Mun yi ƙoƙari mu magance matsalar, mun yi tunanin cewa wata matsala ce ta fasaha.
Amma ba haka ba ne, amma saboda tsarin gwamnati.
Zan iya yi muku alkawari cewa ba zai sake faruwa ba a gaba.
Za mu rage zuwa wasanni biyar maimakon shida kamar yadda muka saba, kuma mun yi ƙoƙari mu ba wa magoya baya ƙarin, kuma mun wuce iyaka.
Wannan mummunan yanayi ne.
Tom Daley ya ji "ƙananan" saboda jima'i
Mai wasan ruwa na Olympics Tom Daley ya ce ya girma yana jin cewa shi ya fi kowa daraja saboda jima'i, amma hakan ya sa ya yi nasara.
Dan wasan mai shekara 24 ya ce bai fahimci hakan ba sai da ya shiga makaranta cewa "ba kowa ba ne kamar ni".
Ya kasance baƙo a farkon shirin Desert Island Discs wanda Lauren Laverne ya gabatar a Radio 4, ya ce yana magana ne game da haƙƙin 'yan luwadi don ba wasu "bege".
Ya kuma ce sa'ad da ya zama mahaifi, ba ya son gasar Olympics sosai.
Kirsty Young, wadda ta saba gabatar da shirin, za ta yi wata biyu ba ta halarta ba saboda rashin lafiya.
Da aka gayyace shi zuwa ga Laverne na farko, Daley ya ce lokacin da yake yaro ya ji "ƙananan" ga wasu saboda "ba shi da kyau a cikin al'umma don in so yara maza da mata".
Ya ce, "Har zuwa yanzu, waɗannan ƙarancin jin daɗi da jin banbanci, sune ainihin abubuwan da suka ba ni ƙarfi da juriya don samun nasara".
Ya so ya tabbatar da cewa shi "wani ne", in ji shi, don kada ya sa kowa ya yi baƙin ciki lokacin da suka san game da jima'i.
Wanda ya lashe lambar tagulla ta Olympics sau biyu ya zama sanannen mai ba da shawara ga kamfen na LGBT kuma ya yi amfani da fitowar da ya yi a wasannin Commonwealth na wannan shekara a Ostiraliya don neman ƙarin ƙasashe su dakatar da luwadi.
Ya ce ya yanke shawarar yin magana ne domin yana jin cewa yana da sa'a ya rayu cikin 'yanci, ba tare da wata matsala ba, kuma yana so ya ba wasu 'bege'.
Gwarzon zakaran duniya sau uku ya ce ya yi mamakin yadda ya ƙaunaci wani mutum, fim din Amurka Dustin Lance Black.
Daley ta yi aure a bara da fim din da ya lashe lambar yabo ta Oscar, wanda ya girme shi da shekaru 20, amma ya ce bambancin shekaru bai taba zama matsala ba.
"Lokacin da ka sha wahala sosai a wannan lokacin" - ya halarci gasar Olympics ta farko lokacin da yake ɗan shekara 14 kawai, kuma mahaifinsa ya mutu daga ciwon kansa bayan shekaru uku - ya ce, yana da wuya a sami wani a shekarunsa wanda ya sha wahala da kuma wahala.
A watan Yuni, sun haifi ɗa mai suna Robert Ray Black-Daley, kuma hakan ya canja "tunani" da Daley ya yi.
"Idan an tambaye ni a bara, ba ni da sha'awar komai sai lashe lambar zinare", in ji shi.
Akwai abubuwa da suka fi zinare muhimmanci a gasar Olympics.
Robbie ne zinaren zinariyar Olympics.
