Jami'an diflomasiyyar sun lura cewa Jamhuriyar Dominica da Panama sun riga sun amince da Beijing, tare da rashin adawa daga Washington.
Trump ya yi wata ganawa ta maraba da shugaban Jamhuriyar Panama, Juan Carlos Varela a watan Yunin 2017 kuma ya mallaki wani otal a Panama har sai abokan hulɗar sun kwashe ƙungiyar jagorancin Trump Organization.
