Amma a tsakiyar watan Satumba, manyan jami'an gwamnati sun bayyana a fili cewa suna son ci gaba da taron, suna kammala duk wani nazari kan takunkumi ga El Salvador.
Yanzu haka ana shirin mataimakin shugaban kasa Mike Pence ya yi jawabi a taron, wanda aka shirya yi a tsakiyar watan Oktoba, yana so ya nuna muhimmancin da gwamnatin ke ba taron, in ji jami'an diflomasiyya.
Kuma jakadun Amurka uku sun koma cikin nutsuwa zuwa El Salvador, Panama da Jamhuriyar Dominica, ba tare da karɓar sabbin sakonni ko tsauraran matakai daga Washington ba.
