Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a ƙasar Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu sakamakon wata girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske da tsunami da ta afkawa garin Palu na Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, a cewar hukumomi, kuma ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu.
Saboda katsewar hanyoyin sadarwa, hukumomin da ke kula da bala'in ba su iya samun wani bayani daga Donggala Regency, wani yanki a arewacin garin Palu, wanda ya fi kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasa mai girman 7.5 a kan ma'aunin Richter.
A Palu, an kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 bayan bala'in.
Ga wasu abubuwa masu muhimmanci game da Palu da Donggala a Sulawesi:
Palu babban birnin lardin tsakiyar Sulawesi ne, wanda ke kan iyakar wani kunkuru a gabar yammacin Sulawesi, wanda ke da mazaunan kusan 379,800 a shekarar 2017.
Birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafuwa lokacin da tsunami da girgizar kasa suka afkawa.
Donggala wani yanki ne da ke kan iyakar bakin teku mai nisan kilomita 300 a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
A cikin shekarar 2017, yawan jama'ar yankin ya kai 299,200.
Aikin kiwon kifi da aikin gona sune cibiyar tattalin arzikin lardin tsakiyar Sulawesi, musamman yankin Donggala.
Har ila yau, ayyukan hakar ma'adinai don hakar ma'adinai suna da muhimmanci a lardin, amma an fi mayar da hankali a Morowali, a gefen tekun Sulawesi.
Palu da Donggala sun sha fama da tsunami sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, a cewar Hukumar Kula da Bala'o'i ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya lalata ɗaruruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Hakanan a cikin 1996, tsunami ya afku a yammacin yankin Donggala, wanda ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin da ake yawan girgizar ƙasa a cikin tekun Pacific.
Ga wasu daga cikin girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka faru a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: A ranar 26 ga Disamba, wata babbar girgizar ƙasa a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh na Indonesia, a arewacin tsibirin Sumatra, ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya shafi ƙasashe 14, ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, fiye da rabi daga Aceh.
2005: Ƙarƙashin ƙasa mai ƙarfi ya afku a gabar yammacin tsibirin Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Mutane da yawa sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, a bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 a kan sikelin Richter ta afku a kudancin tsibirin Java mafi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya mamaye gabar kudu, ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.6 a kan ma'aunin Richter ta auku a kusa da birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
Mutane sama da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Wata girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.5 a kan ma'aunin Richter ta afku a tsibirin Mentawai, a gabar tekun Sumatra, ta haifar da tsunami mai tsawon mita 10, wanda ya lalata kauyuka da dama kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016: wata girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afku a yankin Pidie Jaya na Aceh, ta haddasa barna da firgici yayin da mutane ke tuno da girgizar kasa da tsunami mai bala'in gaske da ta afku a shekarar 2004 wanda ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane da dama.
Amma ba a yi tsunami ba, amma mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu saboda gine-ginen da suka rushe.
2018: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afku a tsibirin Lombok, inda ta kashe mutane sama da 500, mafi yawansu a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma dubban masu yawon bude ido sun makale a karkashin tarkace.
