Don tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara dole ne su tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya "da gangan" ya kashe duk wadanda aka kashe takwas kuma ya "da gangan" ya haifar da mummunan rauni, a cewar sanarwar niyyar neman hukuncin kisa da aka gabatar a Kudancin Yankin New York.
Dukkanin masu laifin za su iya fuskantar hukuncin kisa, a cewar takardar kotun.
Makonni bayan harin, wata babbar kotun tarayya ta tuhumi Saipov da laifuka 22 da suka hada da laifuka takwas na kisan kai a cikin kungiyar ta'addanci, wanda yawanci masu gabatar da kara ke amfani da shi a shari'ar ta'addanci, da kuma laifuka daya na tashin hankali da lalata motoci.
Harin ya bukaci "tsari mai zurfi da kuma shiri", in ji masu gabatar da kara, suna bayyana yadda Saipov ya aikata lamarin a matsayin "abin ƙyama, mummunan aiki da lalata".
Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya jawo wa iyalan da abokansa rauni, wahala da asarar abubuwa kamar Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco, a cewar sanarwar.
