An yanke hukuncin kisa a shekarar 1953 a wani shari'ar tarayya a birnin New York, an kashe Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata biyu da aka yanke wa hukuncin kisa bayan an yanke musu hukuncin kisa a kan zargin yin ta'addanci a lokacin Cold War a cikin Soviet Union shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
